thread.title: Drew Cameron

author: Drew Cameron
title: Drew Cameron
text:
I had tried 3 or 4 different Snus websites before finding Snusline, and haven't looked back. I have placed bi-weekly orders for the last year or so and have absolutely no complaints. Packages arrive reliably and within their stated time estimates to Canada.
I would love to see them sell Match products, but the current selection is more than acceptable.
I would (and do) recommend this company to anyone who asks.
